  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.4.6">
<l>paiṅkaṇviṟal cemmukattu vāli māḷap paṭarvaṉattuk kavantaṉoṭum paṭaiyār tiṇkai</l>
<l>veṅkaṇviṟal virātaṉuka viṟku ṉitta viṇṇavarkkōṉ tāḷaṇaivīr veṟpup pōlum</l>
<l>tuṅkamuka māḷikaimē lāyaṅ kūṟun tuṭiyiṭaiyār mukakkamalac cōti taṉṉāl</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷmukam paṉipaṭaikku maḻakār kāḻic cīrāma viṇṇakarē cērmi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who clasp the feet of the celestials’ king who bent the bow</l>
<l rend="indent">so that powerful Virādha, with fierce eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">and strong weapon-filled arms, fell</l>
<l>Along with Kabandha of the expansive forest, [and] so that strong Vāli,</l>
<l rend="indent">with a red face and green eyes, died,</l>
<l>Gather you [all] at Cīrāmaviṇṇakaram in beautiful Kāḻi where the face</l>
<l rend="indent">of the moon yields tears because of the radiance of the lotus[-like] faces</l>
<l>Of those with waists like [hand] drums, who tell [each other] secrets</l>
<l rend="indent">on top of mansions, their high facades like mountains.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
